title: Tiem Chay White Oak Vegetarian Foods Store
description: Asian vegetarian food shop sharing space with a Centre Street Meat shop. There is no sign on the door, and it is not easily visible from street so look for it. Specializing in Chinese & Vietnamese food products, including frozen mock meats and dumplings. The products that are made by the owners are vegan and might include spring rolls and sticky rice packets, but imported items might not be.
